summary: This document is an invoice from FedEx to NYSG LLC detailing transportation and special handling charges for services rendered. It includes information about the billing and shipping addresses, payment due date, and specific charges related to the services provided.
keyFacts: The invoice number is 5-836-06095, dated May 04, 2001.
Total charges on the invoice amount to $48.10.
The payment is due by May 19, 2001.
The invoice includes details about additional handling surcharges effective from April 16, 2001.
The document mentions FedEx's policy changes regarding invoice adjustments.
